node.text:
Tasting new food, experiencing history and wondering why the hell David chose Sherman Oaks over all of this? But for real, congrats on the green card, dude! i’m excited to travel the world with you. Now you can enjoy the smog and traffic and higher taxes as a LEGAL CITIZEN.
// @discoveryplus

node.text: My favorite sports are those that lead you to believe they’ll be played predominately with one anatomical structure only to then be played by another. So you should understand my excitement when I heard FOOTBALL is back, and this season I’ve partnered with DraftKings. Download the @draftkings_sportsbook app and if TB doesn’t lose by 74 points, you WIN. It’s a no brainer. Link in bio #ad
